Package whitecat.core.role.descriptors

Interface Summary
GenericRole This interface defines the base structure of a GenericRole, that is a role that can be used within the RoleX system.
 

Class Summary
AbstractDescriptor The base for all the descriptors tied to roles.
EventDescriptor A descriptor of an event.
OperationDescriptor A descriptor for a role operation.
RoleDescriptor A descriptor for a role instance.
